Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.45,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You guys...what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:22.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:41.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ これは 錯覚ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.48,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.59,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...isn't my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:51.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いる 香織が来ている 香織か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:46.55,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.30,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaori is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.85,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaori is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,香織がきていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.10,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Kaori was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,感じなかったか 涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.12,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Did you sense it, Ryosuke ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.65,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:01.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,感じました 香織さんがいつもつけていた香水の匂いが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.73,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,It was the scent of the \Nperfume she always wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな場所にあるはずのない匂いなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be able to\Nsmell it in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,料金所の手前で 突然車に飛び込んできたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.61,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,...but it suddenly entered \Nmy car before the toll booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:14.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,直感的に思いました 香織さんが来ているんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.26,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I intuitively realized Kaori was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩 俺たち二人は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:21.25,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Senpai, we must have \Nencountered some kind of miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶんちょっとした奇跡に立ち会ったんだと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は彼女の命日なんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:27.47,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Today's her anniversary.\NIt must be Kaori who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩を助けたのは 香織さんなんじゃないんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介 お前はばかじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Ryosuke, are you stupid ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:36.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,明確な殺意を持って俺は後ろを走っていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.71,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,I had solid hostile intent \Nas I drove behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:40.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ間違えていれば おまえは殺人事件被害者なんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:41.50,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{hitotsu}You would've been a murder\Nvictim if the worst happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:44.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに なぜしれっとしていられる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:47.24,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,How can you sound so nonchalant, as if it happened to someone else ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,他人事みたいに語っている場合かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何のことだか分かりませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.90,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.66,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,We just had a "battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはバトルをしただけです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:57.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが俺を本気で殺すつもりなら 簡単なことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:57.65,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,It would've been easy to \Nkill me if you were serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そうはならなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:00.70,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,...but it didn't turn out that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが自分のルールを守っていたからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,...because you followed your own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.99,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,That's why I accepted your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから俺も受けて立った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,持てる能力の全てを出し切って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:11.89,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,We threw everything we had into it,\Nand now both of us are standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは今 ここに立っている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の公道バトルの相手が あなただったことが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:18.02,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{saigo}The fact that you were the opponent for my last\Nstreet battle means more than anything else to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何よりも価値があるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:22.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に 峠の楽しさを教えてくれたのは あなたですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:23.09,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{ore}It was you who taught me the\Njoy of driving the mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩 あなたの前でいい走りができた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:28.29,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{anata}I was able to drive so well with you watching, so I'm satisfied from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心から満足です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:30.57,D-PS-ja,,0,0,0,,说得这么好听 其实是杀人未遂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にとっては それだけでいいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.27,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{ore}That's more than enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.44,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら考えても 答えは出なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:42.30,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure out why, no matter how hard I tried. It was just painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ苦しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:47.59,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{itsumo}I blamed myself every day, and spent a countless number of sleepless nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも自分を責めるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,眠れない夜が果てしなく続いた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ネガティブなイメージだけが膨らんでいくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.70,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{negative}Only the negative images filled my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:56.05,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,But tonight, after racing with you, I feel like \Nsomething inside me was finally able to let go.{But I was able to get over it tonight.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 今夜 お前と走って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが吹っ切れた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.56,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{omoi}It was probably because I was able\Nto express my feelings to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,思いのたけを吐き出すことができたからだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は受け止めてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.26,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{omoi}And you responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:05.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どれほど言葉を連ねるよりも雄弁に伝わってくるものがあったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:06.65,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{dorehodo}Your message was loud and clear,\Nand stronger than any words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:12.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も俺と同じ苦しさを抱えている それがよく分かったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.50,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{omae}I realized so well that you've \Nbeen suffering from the same pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:17.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまなかったな 涼介 感謝している
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.79,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ryosuke. Thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無視しようと思えばそうすることもできたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:22.41,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{mushi }You could have ignored me, but you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は来てくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と走りて満足だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.65,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,I'm satisfied having raced with you. {I'm honestly happy to have\Nbeen able to race with you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.71,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,I can say that from the bottom of my heart.{I'm honestly happy to have\Nbeen able to race with you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心からそういえる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大事な車が擦り傷だらけですね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.97,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Your precious car is scratched up so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:43.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな やむにやまれぬ事情でね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:42.91,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,傷の一つ一つを見れば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:49.99,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,I can imagine how difficult the situation\Nwas just by examining those scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:50.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どれほど苛酷な局面をくぐりぬけてきたのか 想像はつきますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あえて多くはいいません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.89,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,I'm not going to say much.\NI'm just glad you made it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく無事で戻ってきました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:01.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがは高橋涼介 お疲れ様です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:59.00,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,That's the Takahashi Ryosuke I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.61,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:06.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺自身も あの人と走ることによって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:09.06,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I feel like I was able to get \Nover a lot of things by racing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんなものが吐き出せた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分のためのバトルでもあったと思ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.94,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,It was a battle for my own sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.68,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Something's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介さんの表情が前と違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:19.46,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ryosuke's facial expression is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:22.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが吹っ切れたような いい表情になった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.74,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He looks better, as if he feels refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:25.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,チームのリーダーとして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:29.34,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,As a team leader who sends\Ntwo drivers into battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:28.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二人のドライバーを戦いに送り出す立場の俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:33.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最前線のリアルをどんな時も分かっていないといけない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:33.88,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{saizensen}...I must always know the reality of \Nwhat it's like to fight on the frontline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:36.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その部分がぼやけることが一番こわい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:37.70,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{sono}What's most frightening is \Nbecoming less sensitive to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:42.54,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{saishu}But I was able to reassure myself\Nabout my insight before the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:41.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最終戦を前にそこをきっちりと確認することができたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神奈川エリアでもっともリスキーなステージで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:47.81,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{kanagawa}I've done everything I could for\Nthe riskiest stage in Kanagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やれるだけのことはやった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,内のダブルエースはもう俺を超えている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:51.95,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{uchi}Our double-aces have already surpassed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.40,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,They should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの二人なら大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後一戦です 勝ちに行きましょう 全力で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.60,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,One more battle to go.\NLet's do our best to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:09.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いよいよあと一週間か プロジェクトD の神奈川最終戦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:10.16,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,One week until Project D's\Nfinal battle in Kanagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーのダウンヒルはどんなドライバーかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:14.08,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,I wonder what sort of driver\N Sidewinder's downhiller is.{I wonder what kind of downhill\Ndriver Team Sidewinder has.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車種とかも気になるんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.54,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,I'm also curious about what\Nkind of car he's going to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ どんなやつが出てこようが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:21.12,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,Well, whoever he is, \Nhe'll be no match for Takumi.{Well, whoever he is,\NTakumi has no weaknesses.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海に死角はないですけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう思うんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.35,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,That's what I think, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神奈川遠征が始まったばかりのころ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:29.00,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,But remember Kenji mumbling about something just when the Kanagawa battles started ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,健二がぼふっといってたことがあるよな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのコースだけに めちゃめちゃ特化したスペシャリストがいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:35.20,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of a driver who's\Nspecialized in a particular course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりこわいな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:39.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それこそ秋名で連戦連勝してた拓海みたいなイメージの走り屋がさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:39.77,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,The kind of driver like Takumi \Nwho won race after race on Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いないですって そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.36,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海は特別ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:47.63,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,Takumi's one of a kind, because he didn't grow up in an ordinary family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,家庭環境が普通じゃないですから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,親がよっぽと変わりもんじゃないと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.26,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,Parents have to be\Neccentric for that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれはないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.64,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Well that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特別な環境と特別な才能がはぐくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:57.90,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,He's a natural racer with a\Nspecial environment and talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:59.22,D-PS-ja,,0,0,0,,neta:乾信司即拓海最终战对手被称为另一个天然(natural)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,天然のドライバーですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.30,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,You honestly think there's another\Nstrange family like them in Kanagawa ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:01.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな変な親子は神奈川にいるかって話です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:05.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.31,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:20.87,D-PS-ja,,0,0,0,,其实这台车已经不是86了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きたきた  ちょっとうるさい車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.96,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Here comes that "slightly loud" car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,美佳 制服か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.32,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,You're still wearing your uniform, Mika ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:29.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよ だって 帰って着替える時間なかっただもん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:29.53,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Yep. I didn't have time\Nto go home and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,珍しくないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.25,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,It's not that uncommon, right ? {There's nothing unusual about it, is there ?\NYou were wearing a uniform last year.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分だって去年まで制服着てたくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.27,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,I mean, up until last year\Nyou were wearing one, too.{There's nothing unusual about it, is there ?\NYou were wearing a uniform last year.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,似合う 美佳のセーラー服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.70,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Do I look good in the sailor-style uniform ? {I added "style," but "sailor-style" can't be omitted.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の彼女が女子高生だって 実感したでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:50.00,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,You came to realize your girlfriend is a high school girl, didn't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはまぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:55.60,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Well yeah, but you won't be\Nable to play golf that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,, けど それだと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,, 今日は ゴルフは無理だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:58.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,平気だよ 美佳は今日コーチだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.43,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,No worries, because I'm your coach today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また右か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.25,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,To the right again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしても右だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.09,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,It goes to the right no matter what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,曲がるけど よくなったね拓海君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.05,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,It does curve, but you've improved, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.25,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてのころとは別人だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.30,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,You're totally different from the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり男の子って痩せってても力あるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.86,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Even a skinny guy has some muscle, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:43.30,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Maybe. I think my arms are strong\Nbecause of the Eight-Six's steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺結構腕力がある子だと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,86のステアリングで鍛えられているから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:46.04,D-PS-ja,,0,0,0,,祖都是方向盘强度设到10的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,めっちゃ重いんだ あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.90,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,It's so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:49.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,打つときに右手が強いから曲がるんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.40,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,It curves like that because you put\Ntoo much strength in your right arm. {Is this factually correct? Better way to word this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと貸してみて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.61,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,{chotto}Let me use your club for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:56.70,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,When the club is in this position,\Nthe face should look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:56.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラブがこの位置の時は フェースはこうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく分かんないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:11:00.50,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I don't really understand.\NCan you show me how ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,美佳 やって見て
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 後ろから見てて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.80,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Well then, watch me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.30,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.90,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,...and just lift the club naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あとはそのまま 持ち上げるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:29.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,美佳 かわる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.22,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.00,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,...I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,, 打っちゃだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.52,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,You shouldn't.{You should take a shot.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,池谷 イツキ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.00,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,Iketani, Itsuki !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした 健二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.15,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kenji ? You look upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:48.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,血相を変えて ばあちゃんがまた行方不明か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.40,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Did your grandma go missing again ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,返事でもねえこというな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.70,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,Don't go and jinx us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,週末の箱根の最新情報だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.91,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,I've got the latest info on \Nthis weekend's race in Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらず秘密主義で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:58.94,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,They're so secretive, that I don't know much in detail, except for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,詳しいことは何も分からないんだけど 一つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:02.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーのダウンヒル担当ドライバーについての情報が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.97,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,{sidewinder}We didn't know anything about\NSidewinder's downhill driver, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今までなかったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か 分かったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.71,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,What do you know about him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それがさドライバーのことはまだ何も分からないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:10.20,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't know anything\Nabout the driver himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:13.10,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,...but apparently, his car is an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:13.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車が86らしいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ 86
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.50,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,An Eight-Six ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:20.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その86って トレノなんですか レビンなんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:20.73,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,Is it a Trueno or Levin ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまではまだわからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.39,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,I don't know that much yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも そこは重要なとこじゃないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:27.00,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Besides, that's not important, is it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは まぁ 確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.31,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,You're absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,86対86か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.04,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Eight-Six versus Eight-Six, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ラッキーで考えるべきでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:40.25,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,It's fortunate because Takumi won't lose, if both cars are Eight-Sixes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:39.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ86なら 拓海が負けるわけないって言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.54,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be any other Eight-Six drivers who are better than Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:43.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海よりうまい奴なんているわけないですって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:49.80,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,{donna}I was nervous, not knowing what the \Nopponent's car was, but now I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな車種か分からないうちは不安ですだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:49.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これでもう安心ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,テクニック勝負に持ち込めれば 絶対拓海のもんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:54.40,def2,.ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,{technique}Once Takumi engages in a fight of \Ndriving technique, he'll win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,単純にそう考えるのはあまいぞ イツキ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:58.00,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,It's too naive to simplify\Nthe matter like that, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:01.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も同感だな めちゃめちゃいやな感じだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.80,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.54,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,I've a bad feeling because it's so ominous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,, 不気味で仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神奈川最強といわれるサイドワインダーが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:08.95,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,...for Sidewinder, which is the best in Kanagawa, to use an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ86をぶつけてくるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どれだけ自信持ってるかって話だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.83,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,{doredake}It's a matter of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:15.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手方にも物凄く切れる参謀がいるらしいからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.94,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,They appear to have a very good strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:21.60,def2,..KENJI..,0,0,0,,I don't think he staged a battle between two\NEight-Sixes just to make the show more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ盛り上がるためだけに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,86対決を演出してきたわけじゃないだろうし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:25.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プロジェクトDを迎え打つために 万全の準備をしてるはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:26.30,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,They must be doing \Neverything to counter Project D.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海の快進撃を止めるために
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:33.55,def2,.IKETANI.,0,0,0,,Their choice of an Eight-Six as their final weapon to stop Takumi's consecutive wins may be a sign of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:33.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自信を持って送り出してくる 最終兵器が86だってことじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしてみている分には
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:03.38,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,He drives so smoothly that he doesn't leave any strong impression at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:03.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スムーズのだけでこれといったインパクトはないんですわね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでもタイムを計れば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:09.55,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,But if you time him, he drives this downhill \Nfaster than any of the Sidewinder members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーのどのクルマよりも速く下ってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おまけにこのコース以外は走られへんときいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.94,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,Plus, he doesn't drive any other course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.26,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,This world is full of strange talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,世の中には奇妙な素材がおろもんやな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな子供がなぜこれほどの芸当を身につけたんか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.10,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,I wonder how a kid like \Nhim acquired such skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不思議でならんわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.40,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,It's perplexing.{ I'm at a loss.}{so puzzled.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,常識とされているドラテクのセオリーとは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:28.20,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{joshiki}It's something beyond the common notion of what driving technique should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,別のところに存在する なにかや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.32,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,Even Project D will be caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:34.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがのプロジェクトDもドぎも抜かれるで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつが R32を処分したらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.23,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,He got rid of his R32.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつって凛さんのことか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:44.34,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,Do you mean Rin ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.20,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何がきっかけであいつが変わったのかはわからないがな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:50.61,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,I don't know what made him change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:55.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死神GTRが箱根に出没することはもう二度とない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:56.34,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,The Grim Reaper GT-R will \Nnever appear in Hakone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう風のふきまわしか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.55,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,以前の職場に復職ねがいが出されているそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:02.20,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,...but I've heard that he's requested\Nto return his former position at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北条家にとってはいいことじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.10,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,It's good for the Hojo family, isn't it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかもしれないが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:08.78,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Probably so, but it\Ndoesn't mean anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にとっちゃどうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:13.55,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Little kids maybe, but we're not at the age where we can \Njust up and go back to being friendly siblings just like that.{We're no longer kids. We can't just return to being friendly siblings of some sort.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキならともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら兄弟仲良くって年でもないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いい年して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:19.44,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's creepy for brothers\Nour age{grown-ups}{brothers} to be so clingy.{I can't be worried about \Neverything my brother does.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アニキアニキってのもきもいだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何がプロジェクトDだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.55,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Project D, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:24.55,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll defeat you, Takahashi Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:24.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が止めらせ 高橋啓介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうですか 新しいセットアップは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.40,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,How is the new setup ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,赤城道路だといい感じだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.25,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,It feels good on Akagi's roads...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:40.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,箱根に乗り込んでデータを採ってみないと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:42.25,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,...but I can't say much until\Nwe get some data in Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんともいえないな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早いとこ最終ステージのコースを攻めたいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:47.93,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,I want to tackle the final stage real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,イメージトレーニングはもうやりあきてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.65,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,I'm tired of image training.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:17.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,箱根遠征の間 カレンダーにまるつけておくから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:17.65,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I'll circle the dates of my Hakone\Nexpeditionary race on the calendar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,配達の日付間違えんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.65,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,...so don't forget your \Ndelivery dates, okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.35,def2,..BUNTA..,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえもんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.20,def2,..BUNTA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}His tire management is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このタイヤの使い方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:35.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けどひっかかるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.65,def2,..BUNTA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But something bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コントロールできすぎなとこが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:38.40,def2,..BUNTA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The control is too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,啓介 藤原 きてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.31,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Keisuke, Fujiwara, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってると思うけど 今回のコースは長い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:56.73,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,As you know, this course is long, so it's physically impossible to practice on everything in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:56.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一日のプラクティスですべてをつめていくのは物理的に無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.22,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,So cut it to the bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから思い切って絞り込め
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:03.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負どころだと感じるポイントを走りながら自分で見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:05.25,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{shobu}Find what will become the key to victory as \Nyou drive, then expand your scope from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから広げていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全部やろうと思えば中途半端なものになる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.33,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{zenbu}If you try to do everything,\Nit'll only be half finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,明日のドッグファイトをイメージしながら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:13.87,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{ahita}Imagine tomorrow's dogfight, and take a practical\Nstrategy of knowing what to focus on and what not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,メリハリをつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実戦的な攻撃で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たちにはそれができるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.15,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I'm sure both of you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よし いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.14,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Then go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コース長いからな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:37.84,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,The course is so long that it'll take longer than usual to complete their routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:37.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ルーティンをこなすだけで いつもより時間がかかるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,日の出まではみっちり走りこませるから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.25,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I'm going to let them practice \Nthoroughly until dawn, so be prepared.\N{We'll let them take plenty of time for driving until the dawn. Okay ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:40.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たのむぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:41.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.30,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.20,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I'll get more food\Nthan usual for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:45.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもより多めに 夜食の買出しをしておくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,腹がへっちゃ 戦はできないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:48.30,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,They say you can't fight\Non an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.75,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fumihiro.\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな 史浩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りにしてるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのさ 松本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:59.77,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Hey, Matsumoto, you\Nknow something, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おまえ何か知ってるんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:00.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにをですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.16,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,About what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介のことに決まってるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:06.27,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,About Ryosuke, of course. \NHe's acting differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か雰囲気が違うんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ まぁ 最終戦ですからね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.20,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Well, it must be because\Nthis is the final battle. {Well, it must be because of the final battle.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.45,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,集中してると思いますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そういうんじゃないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:13.63,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か吹っ切れた感じっていうのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:19.63,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,, It's like he's relaxed,\Nlike he's smiling more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前よりも笑うっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぁ 松本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.91,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, if you know something, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知っているなら教えてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さぁ 何も知らないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.20,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.10,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,...I don't know anything, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分で聞いてみたらどうです 直接本人に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.55,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask him yourself ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どう思う 久保さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.84,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kubo ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:39.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうのFD 前回のスパイラル戦の時とイメージが違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.65,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,That FD is giving off a different feeling from the last battle against Spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:44.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の決戦に向けて かなりいじってきたのかもしれないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:44.31,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,It might have been \Nmodified a lot for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:46.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうですかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.10,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,カーボンのフードに換えてきたんで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:51.25,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,The outer appearance is different \Nbecause of the carbon fiber hood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見た目のイメージは変わりましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:54.76,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,...but the insides shouldn't have changed much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中身はそう大きくは換えんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気になるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.70,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,I'm worried. Forget about the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,86はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:00.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,FDのデータを集中的に集めるように指示してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:01.41,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Instruct everyone to focus \Ntheir data collection on the FD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やれと言われればやりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.45,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,If you say so, I'll do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本間に86はいいんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.61,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,...but are you sure about the Eight-Six ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,シンジの走りにデータは無意味だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.79,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Data is meaningless for Shinji's driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:14.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あってもそれを生かせないし なくても必ず勝つだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.90,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,He won't be able to make use of the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.55,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't have it, he'll still win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:19.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,シンジはそういうドライバーだ ちがうか 久保さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:20.05,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Shinji is that kind of driver.\NDon't you think so too, Kubo ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちがわんでしょうな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.30,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,FDを集中的にたのむ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.01,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Focus on the FD.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:30.57,def2,...GOU...,0,0,0,,Obtain as much information on its section times\Nto determine how its fighting potential varies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,区間タイムをなるべく多く集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,戦闘力の変化をきっちり見極めてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わかりました 手配しましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.58,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll arrange that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やれやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:42.80,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Oh man, our boss is nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ナーバスになっとる うちの大将は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:46.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手方の陽動作戦に見事にのせられとるがな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:46.29,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He fell for our opponent's diversion strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:52.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来て大きくスペックを変えるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.70,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}They shouldn't have changed the \Nspecs very drastically at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:56.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのFDはもう完成してバランスがとれている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:57.30,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That FD is a completely balanced machine.{That FD is a balanced complete machine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はだまされんぞ 高橋涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:01.28,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I won't be tricked, Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたとの知恵くらべや相手にとって不足はない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:07.30,def2,..KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is our match of intelligence.\NYou're worthy of being my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よ ゼロの兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.83,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:20.08,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't the hot-blooded 246 guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かと思えば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,246の熱血アニキじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いよいよ来るところまできたって感じだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.40,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,It has finally come to the \Nmoment of truth, hasn't it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の予想では
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:28.16,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,I was expecting you to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたのところで止めてくれると思ってたんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな 力不足で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.35,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,Sorry that we weren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高橋啓介 どんなドライバーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.65,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,Takahashi Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.26,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,How do you rate him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:46.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハーフウエットでのアクセルコントロールが抜群にうまかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:47.91,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,His accelerator technique on \Na half-wet road was exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:54.44,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,He managed to control the traction of the \Nrear tires, as if they were a part of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:51.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リアタイヤに体の神経が同調しているかのような
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トラクションのコントロールができていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:58.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負どころでの集中力というか きりかえもすごい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:59.30,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{shobu}Besides his concentration right at the moment of attack,\Nhis ability to switch mindsets quickly is also impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブースターに点火したジェット戦闘機のような
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:06.28,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{booster}He reaches beyond the scope of Zero Theory, like a fighter jet boosted by an afterburner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:05.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゼロ理論ではありえない領域に入っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:11.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりあんたに似たタイプかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.84,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,In other words, he's like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:12.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:12.70,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,Like me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,闘争心をむき出しにして乗っていくタイプだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:18.05,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,The type of driver who shows his eagerness for \Nvictory, who has skills and understands the theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,技術もあるし理屈もわかっているが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最後は気持ちで行く感覚派だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.76,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,But in the end, what\N matters most is the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:24.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたと高橋啓介はそういうところが似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:24.10,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,You and Takahashi Keisuke\Nare alike on that account.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ふうん 悪い気はしないがね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.83,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,I don't feel bad hearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.45,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,What kind of driver is Fujiwara Takumi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原拓海は どんなドライバーだい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:41.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたに聞いておきたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:45.02,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,I want to hear your opinion since you witnessed his true{real} potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:44.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一番リアルなところを見てきているわけだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは表現するのがむずかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.70,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,It's difficult to describe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.47,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,It's like a black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:50.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まるでブラックホールとでもいうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.30,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,Black hole ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブラックホール
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:55.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでも貪欲にほうりこんでいくスペースの広さがある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:56.21,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,He has a wide margin to be able to absorb a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:59.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,かたくななまでに自分のスタイルがあるようでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:22:03.09,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,He appears to have his own concrete policy, but in\Nreality, he has no color. He's transparent and flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は無色透明で柔軟だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:05.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一戦ごとに確実に成長しているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:11.25,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,He improves race after race, so he's probably different from when he raced against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:09.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん俺が戦った時のあいつと今のあいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:11.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう同じじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:13.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高い評価だな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:15.35,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,So you think highly of him, \Nalmost raving about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶賛じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:18.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それならばプロジェクトＤ対サイドワインダー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:20.52,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{sore}Then what's your prediction for this\Nbattle between Project D and Sidewinder ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:20.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この対決 どううらなう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:21.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ザックリと来たな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.40,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,You want to cut to\Nthe point, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:24.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ではあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.90,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:27.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーが勝つだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:26.80,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,...but Sidewinder will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も同じ答えだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:34.86,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,I've come to the same answer.\NI really admire Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:34.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は高橋涼介という男にホレこんでいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:38.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神奈川エリアの一員としては大きな声では言えないが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:41.50,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,As a member of a Kanagawa area team, I can't openly say this, but my emotional side wants Project D to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.02,0:22:41.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心情的にはプロジェクトＤに勝たせたいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:42.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:43.69,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,But that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:46.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーには十分な時間があった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:46.90,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,Sidewinder had plenty of time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:49.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,久保英次という参謀がついているかぎり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:51.32,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,As long as they have Kubo Eiji as their\N strategist, they don't have any weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死角はない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:54.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 勝負はやってみなければわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:54.90,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,But you can't really tell \Nuntil they start racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プロジェクトＤが勝つ可能性がないわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:58.61,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,It's not like Project D \Nhas no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:01.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドライバーの成長がわずかな希望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:01.55,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,{driver}They have a slight chance due\Nto their drivers' improvements.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる確率は 五分の一ってとこか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:08.65,def2,..OMIYA..,0,0,0,,I say their chance of winning\Nis one-fifth, which is 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:08.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,20パーセント程度の勝算ということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか偉いことになってるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:13.38,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,This is getting ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:18.65,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,I've never seen so many \Nguys with stopwatches before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:16.25,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今までと比べものにならないくらいの人数が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:18.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ストップウォッチもって立ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:20.98,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Don't they have anything else to do ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:20.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ暇なのって話だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それをいうなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:27.22,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, we aren't that different, coming all the way from Gunma only to race in Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:26.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ群馬から箱根まで峠攻めに来る俺たちも同じだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それもそうだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:29.65,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:31.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,区間タイム計られてるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:34.36,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,They're measuring my\Nsection times pretty closely.{They're measuring my section times using the finely-divided segments.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,かなり細かく区切ってやってる感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:36.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それもちょっとイヤだな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:38.50,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I don't like them trying\Nto figure out our strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:38.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちの手の内をさぐられるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,カムフラージュのパターンを１枚ふやそうか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:41.90,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Should I add another camouflage pattern ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはしない いつもと同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.10,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,No, don't.\NJust do as normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘタに動いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:50.54,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that you won't finish \Npractice if you try to do it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:49.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プラクティスが不十分な終わり方をすることの方がこわい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:51.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来れば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:54.10,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{koko}At this point, we don't\Nhave to modify our style.{\Nto change our normal style.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ふだんどおりの俺達のスタイルはくずさない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:55.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:56.60,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.34,0:23:58.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜいおがませてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:24:02.17,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,I'll let them watch and learn the style of \NProject D, the best of the northern Kanto area.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:24:01.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北関東最強のプロジェクトＤのスタイルを
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:04.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ そういう意味だ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:04.59,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Yup, that's exactly what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:06.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしますか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:07.49,def2,...MAN...,0,0,0,,What should I do then ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,足回りはCパターンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:10.99,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Set the suspension to pattern C,\Nand add 10 liters of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:11.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガソリンも10リッター足してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:16.28,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついたか 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:19.80,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Did you notice a huge number\Nof scouts throughout the course ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.67,0:24:19.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コースのあちこちに偵察舞台がすごいんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:24.85,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Keisuke told me about them,\Nand tons of stopwatches, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:22.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,啓介が言っていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:25.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すごい数のストップウォッチだってさ ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:25.51,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:29.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 確かに人はたくさんいるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:31.30,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,There're quite a lot of people out there, but they aren't pushing the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:31.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,押してないですよ ボタン
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.77,0:24:37.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,１戦目から タイム計ってメモとかしてる人達いたんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:37.82,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I noticed those who were keeping \Ntime and taking notes from the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.69,0:24:39.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん同じ人達だと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:42.45,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,{tabun}I'm sure they're the same people. I remember some of their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.04,0:24:41.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見おぼえある顔いましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:44.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも今日はボタン押してないですね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.45,0:24:45.08,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,But today none of them pressed\Nthe button on their stopwatches.{\NBut today, they weren't keeping time.}{recording times.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:46.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かか 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.08,0:24:46.43,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Fujiwara ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.43,0:24:47.00,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.43,0:24:47.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.47,0:24:50.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,走りながら そんなとこまで気がついてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.66,0:24:51.00,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He noticed such small{minor}\Ndetails while he was driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:53.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつが すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:53.50,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's what makes him so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもどういうことかな涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.85,0:24:59.81,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,But what's the meaning of this, Ryosuke ? \NIt contradicts what Keisuke said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.02,0:24:59.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,啓介の話とちがってるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.62,0:25:00.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:03.65,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,That's fine. Both of \Nthem are telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.84,0:25:03.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,２人が言っていることはそれぞれ正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.64,0:25:04.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,想定どおりさ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:04.88,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,It's going as planned.
