Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.20,0:26:01.74,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{Kazoekirenai hodo no zanzo)}Countless number of memorable scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.37,0:26:04.02,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,数え切れないほどの残像 ギャンブル生き抜いてきた残党
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.74,0:26:04.14,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{??? ikinuite kita zattou}We lived through the hustle and bustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.02,0:26:09.25,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,時に戦い 時に解りあい きれい事ばかりじゃなかった真実
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.14,0:26:06.48,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{toki ni tatakai toki ni wakari ai}Sometimes we argued, sometimes we understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.48,0:26:09.28,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{kireigoto bakari ja nakatta shinjitsu}It wasn't always pretty, but I keep the truth to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.25,0:26:11.70,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,背負ったまま新たな一歩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.28,0:26:12.21,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{shotta mama arata na ippo}...as I take a new step.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.12,0:26:22.70,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,あかね雲が街を染める この行く先をそっと問いかけて見る
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.21,0:26:16.96,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{Akane gumo ga machi wo someru}Rosy clouds embellish the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.96,0:26:22.99,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{Kono yuku saki wo sotto toitakete miru}I quietly ask about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.82,0:26:35.78,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,空はなにもいわず だけど私にこの道を照らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.99,0:26:26.76,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{Sora wa nani mo iwazu}The sky remains silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.76,0:26:36.10,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{dakedo watashi ni kono michi wo terashiteiru}Only illuminating this path before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.78,0:26:38.61,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,透き通る景色を感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.10,0:26:38.76,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{sukitooru keshiki wo kanjite}Feel the translucent scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.91,0:26:43.72,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,旋律を夕陽が奏で
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.93,0:26:43.21,Karaoke Translation op,.EDSONG2.,0,0,0,,{senritsu wo yuuhi ga kanadete}The setting sun plays a melody.
